<p>The idea that some invisible unknown force is acting upon entities far away is rather a magical idea if you think about it.
The idea that the position of the moon influences events on earth sounds just like astrology as it does physics. The only difference is that the claim by physics can be replicated while the one by astrology cannot. But both are equally mystical.</p>

